Semi Realistic AMX 30 DCA Sight (1080p-720p)

This is my first attempt at making a custom sight from scratch, using a French government public defense archive video as reference. The reference is of the AMX 13 DCA which uses the same turret as the AMX 30 DCA from in game.

I added a smol dot in the middle of the crosshair to make it more usable in game, so it's not totally realistic.

#realistic #semi_realistic #historical #amx_30_dca #spaa #aa #crosshair #france
